Package com.manager

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NotificationManager
    Manages the creation and movement of Notifications.
    QueueManager
    A NotificationManager which slides old Notifications above or below new Notifications.
    SimpleManager
    Simply displays new Notifications in one corner of the screen on top of each other.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    QueueManager.ScrollDirection
    Which way the new Notifications scroll.
